rline;">from 512MB to 1GB</span>.</strong></p>\n<p>We&#8217;ve estimated that the typical full WP site backup is about 150MB. You could safely store 6 full site backups plus a dozen other database-only backups with your free Stash storage.</p>\n<h6>So if you aren&#8217;t using BackupBuddy Stash now for your remote backup destination, here&#8217;s a quick video on how to use BackupBuddy Stash:</h6>\n<p><iframe src="http://player.vimeo.com/video/59949776" height="281" width="500" allowfullscreen="" frameborder="0"></iframe></p>\n<h3><img class="alignnone" alt="Divider" src="http://ithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Screen_shot_2012_05_31_at_11_2.38.04_AM.png" width="576" height="13" /></h3>\n<h3>Get 50% Off Extra BackupBuddy Stash Storage</h3>\n<p>For our awesome BackupBuddy customers, we&#8217;re also offering 50% off our <a href="http://ithemes.com/backupbuddy-stash/">BackupBuddy Stash storage packages</a> through midnight (CST) March 31, 2013.</p>\n<p>Simply use <a href="http://ithemes.com/backupbuddy-stash/">BUBSTASH50</a> and choose your BackupBuddy Stash plan after <a href="http://ithemes.com/member/login.php">logging in to your member panel</a>.</p>\n<p><a class="btn green" href="http://ithemes.com/backupbuddy-stash/">Upgrade your BackupBuddy Stash</a></p>\n<h3><img alt="Divider" src="http://ithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Screen_shot_2012_05_31_at_11_2.38.04_AM.png" width="576" height="13" /></h3>\n<h3>Get 33% Off Any BackupBuddy Package</h3>\n<p>If you don&#8217;t have a complete backup strategy for your WordPress site … I have to ask … what are you waiting for?</p>\n<p>Get 33% off all BackupBuddy plans by using <a href="http://ithemes.com/purchase/backupbuddy/">3BACKUP33</a> through March 31, 2013 at midnight CST.</p>\n<p><a class="btn blue" href="http://ithemes.com/purchase/backupbuddy/">Get BackupBuddy today!</a></p>\n<h3><img alt="Divider" src="http://ithemes.com/wp-content/uploads/2013/03/Screen_shot_2012_05_31_at_11_2.38.04_AM.png" width="576" height="13" /></h3>\n<h3>3 Years In &#8230; But We&#8217;re Not Done Improving For You</h3>\n<p>As you are well aware, BackupBuddy <a href="http://ithemes.com/category/backupbuddy/">keeps getting better and better with new features and enhancements</a> to help you easily get your sites backed up.</p>\n<p>Last year we did a customer survey and many of you responded with feedback and insight on how to make BackupBuddy even better.</p>\n<p>Dustin, Jeremy and the BackupBuddy team have already implemented a ton of those great ideas to date.</p>\n<p>And more is on the way! We&#8217;re busy planning for BackupBuddy 4.0 release this summer and taking it farther and farther for you.</p>\n<h3>Tweet About BackupBuddy</h3>\n<p>If you&#8217;ve gotten as much value out of BackupBuddy like thousands of others have and want to say thanks or congrats, please take a second and tweet about it:</p>\n<p>#BackupBuddy rocks &#8211; now with 1GB of free storage for your WordPress backups!<br />\n<a class="twitter-share-button" href="https://twitter.com/share" data-url="http://getbackupbuddy.com" data-text="#BackupBuddy rocks - now with 1GB of free storage for your WordPress backups." data-size="large" data-count="none">Tweet</a><br />\n<script type="text/javascript">// <![CDATA[\n!function(d,s,id){var js,fjs=d.getElementsByTagName(s)[0];if(!d.getElementById(id)){js=d.createElement(s);js.id=id;js.src="//platform.twitter.com/widgets.js";fjs.parentNode.insertBefore(js,fjs);}}(document,"script","twitter-wjs");\n// ]]&gt;</script></p>\n<p>or</p>\n<p>#BackupBuddy launched 3 years ago and is still the best way to backup and move WordPress.<br />\n<a class="twitter-share-button" href="https://twitter.com/share" data-url="http://getbackupbuddy.com" data-text="#BackupBuddy launched 3 years ago and is still the best way to backup and move WordPress." data-size="large" data-count="none">Tweet</a><br />\n<script type="text/javascript">// <![CDATA[\n!function(d,s,id){var js,fjs=d.getElementsByTagName(